<p><a name="Single_account_bookkeeping" id="Single_account_bookkeeping"></a></p>
<h4><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bookkeeping&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: Single account bookkeeping">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Single account bookkeeping</span></h4>
<p>Simple bookkeeping for individuals and families involves recording income, expenses and current balance in a cash record book or a checking account register.</p>
